{{Infobox football biography |name = Ahmet Haliti |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = Ahmet Haliti |birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1988|9|29|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Podujevo]], [[Socialist Federal Republic of Yugoslavia|SFR Yugoslavia]] |height = |position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]] |currentclub = [[FC Prishtina|Prishtina]] |clubnumber = 8 |years1 = 2009–2013 |clubs1 = [[KF Hysi|Hysi]] |caps1 = |goals1 =<!--Appearances and goals with Hysi are missing--> |years2 = 2014 |clubs2 = [[Besa Kavajë]] |caps2 = 14 |goals2 = 1 |years3 = 2014–2015 |clubs3 = [[FC Prishtina|Prishtina]] |caps3 = 24 |goals3 = 1 |years4 = 2015–2016 |clubs4 = [[KF Bylis Ballsh|Bylis Ballsh]] |caps4 = 14 |goals4 = 0 |years5 = 2016–2018 |clubs5 = [[KF Feronikeli|Feronikeli]] |caps5 = 43 |goals5 = 0 |years6 = 2018– |clubs6 = [[FC Prishtina|Prishtina]] |caps6 = 0 |goals6 = 0 <!-- Don't add parameter unless he debuted with national team. |nationalyears1 = 2018– |nationalteam1 = [[Kosovo national football team|Kosovo]] |nationalcaps1 = 0 |nationalgoals1 = 0 --> |club-update = 18 November 2017 |nationalteam-update = 22 January 2018 }} '''Ahmet Haliti''' (born 29 September 1988) is a [[Kosovo Albanian]] professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for Kosovan club [[FC Prishtina|Prishtina]].
==Club career== ===Besa Kavajë=== On 18 January 2014, Haliti signed to [[Albanian Superliga]] side [[Besa Kavajë]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.arkivalajmeve.com/Zyrtare--Ahmet-Haliti-nga-KF-Hysi-transferohet-tek-Besa-e-Kavajes.1047509222/|title=Zyrtare: Ahmet Haliti nga KF Hysi transferohet tek Besa e Kavajës|trans-title=Official: Ahmet Haliti from FC Hysi transfers in Besa Kavajë|website=Arkiva e lajmeve|language=Albanian|date=18 January 2014}}</ref> On 1 February 2014, he made his debut in a 2–2 home draw against [[KF Laçi|Laçi]] after being named in the starting line-up. <!--------------------------------- ===Prishtina=== {{Empty section|date=January 2018}} ----------------------------------> ===Bylis Ballsh=== On 13 August 2015, Haliti signed to [[Albanian Superliga]] side [[Bylis Ballsh]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://sportal.al/haliti-jam-i-bylisit-besoj-te-skuadra/|title=Haliti: Jam i Bylisit, besoj te skuadra|trans-title=Haliti: I'm Bylisi, I believe in the team|website=SportAL|language=Albanian|date=13 August 2015}}</ref> On 23 August 2015, he made his debut in a 2–0 away defeat against [[FK Kukësi|Kukësi]] after being named in the starting line-up.
===Feronikeli=== On 27 May 2016, Haliti signed to [[Football Superleague of Kosovo]] side [[KF Feronikeli|Feronikeli]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.insajderi.com/zyrtare-ferronikeli-transferon-dy-futbolliste-nga-kampionati-shqiptar/|title=Zyrtare: Ferronikeli transferon dy futbollistë nga kampionati shqiptar|trans-title=Official: Ferronikeli transfers two footballers from Albanian championship|website=Insajderi|language=Albanian|date=27 May 2016}}</ref>
===Return to Prishtina=== On 28 May 2018, Haliti returned to [[Football Superleague of Kosovo]] club [[FC Prishtina|Prishtina]] after playing for [[KF Feronikeli|Feronikeli]] for three years, where he signed a one year contract with the club.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://futbollikosovar.com/zyrtare-prishtina-prezanton-super-perforcimin-e-pare-foto/|title=Zyrtare: Prishtina prezanton super-përforcimin e parë (Foto)|trans-title=Official: Prishtina presents first super-reinforcement|website=Futbolli Kosovar|language=Albanian|date=28 May 2018}}</ref>
==International career== On 22 January 2018. Haliti received a call-up from [[Kosovo national football team|Kosovo]] for the [[Exhibition game|friendly match]] against [[Azerbaijan national football team|Azerbaijan]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.korneri.net/lajmi-i-fundit-lista-e-kosoves-kunder-azerbeixhanit/|title=Lajmi i fundit: Lista e Kosovës kundër Azerbajxhanit|trans-title=Latest news: List of Kosovo against Azerbaijan|website=Korneri|language=Albanian|date=22 January 2018}}</ref> The match however was cancelled two days later, which prolonged his debut.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.affa.az/index.php/news/friendly-match-cancelled/61160|title=Friendly match cancelled|publisher=[[Association of Football Federations of Azerbaijan]]|date=25 January 2018}}</ref>
