{{short description|Mountaineering institute in Manali, Himachal Pradesh, India}} {{Multiple issues|{{notability|1=Companies|date=November 2018}}{{advert|date=November 2018}}}}
[[File:Skiing Centre - Atal Bihari Vajpayee Institute of Mountaineering and Allied Sports - Solang Valley - Kullu 2014-05-10 2555.JPG|250px|thumb|Skiing Centre - Atal Bihari Vajpayee Institute of Mountaineering and Allied Sports - [[Solang Valley]], [[Kullu district|Kullu]]]] '''Atal Bihari Vajpayee Institute of Mountaineering and Allied Sports''' (abbreviated to '''ABVIMAS'''<ref>{{cite news |title=Finally, skiing season begins in Himachal Pradesh |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/shimla/finally-skiing-season-begins-in-himachal-pradesh/articleshow/62914435.cms |publisher=[[Times of India]] |date=February 14, 2018}}</ref>) is an Indian institute, which provides specialized training in [[skiing]], [[mountain rescue]] and [[mountaineering]],<ref>{{cite news |title=Grass skiing does not click on Solang slopes |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/grass-skiing-does-not-click-on-solang-slopes/articleshow/63873541.cms |publisher=[[Times of India]] |date=April 24, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=No snow, no skiing in Solang Valley |url=https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/himachal/no-snow-no-skiing-in-solang-valley/535172.html |publisher=[[Tribune India]] |date=January 29, 2018}}</ref> founded in 1961.<ref>{{cite news |title=Come, Ski Down Himachal's Grassy Slopes |url=https://www.mid-day.com/articles/come-ski-down-himachal-s-grassy-slopes/170042 |publisher=[[Mid Day]] |date=June 27, 2012}}</ref> The institute is located in [[Manali, Himachal Pradesh]].
== History == In 1961, it was set up as the Western Himalayan Mountaineering Institute, but later it was renamed after former [[PM of India]], [[Atal Bihari Vajpayee]].<ref>{{cite book |author1=Roshen Dalal |title=India at 70: snapshots since Independenc |publisher=[[Penguin Random House]] |isbn=9789386815378 |url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=JYswDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT92&lpg=PT92&dq=Atal+Bihari+Vajpayee+Institute+of+Mountaineering+and+Allied+Sports+%221961%22&source=bl&ots=7a9APSikcR&sig=rI9s7vKLSZjyGIKEk_2hbGOQ2-c&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj0pafD7dDdAhUXfysKHRE5BCo4ChDoATAFegQIBhAB#v=onepage&q=Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Institute%20of%20Mountaineering%20and%20Allied%20Sports%20%221961%22&f=false}}</ref>
== Courses == ABVIMAS offers mountaineering, skiing and water sports courses.<ref>{{cite web |title=Everything you need to know about mountaineering institutes and courses in India |url=https://www.girlonthemountains.com/single-post/2018/08/03/Everything-you-need-to-know-about-mountaineering-institutes-and-courses-in-India |website=girlonthemountains.com |date=August 3, 2018}}</ref> * Advance Mountaineering Course * Advance Skiing Course * Method of Instruction (Skiing) Course * Intermediate Water Sports Course (White Water Kayaking) & Advance Water Sports Course (Sailing) * Intermediate water Sports Course * Advance Water Sports Course (White Water Kayaking) * Advance Water Sports * Method of Instruction (Water Sports Course)
