'''Copa João Havelange Group Blue''' was one of the three groups of 2000 season's first stage of the [[Campeonato Brasileiro Série A]] [[association football|football]] league, named [[Copa João Havelange]]. It consists of 25 teams, 12 teams qualified to the final stages.
