The '''Indonesian Cycling Federation''' or '''ISSI''' (in [[Indonesian language|Indonesian]]: ''Ikatan Sepeda Sport Indonesia'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Indonesia]].

The ISSI is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Asian Cycling Confederation|ACC]].

