'''Killarney Racecourse''' is a [[horse racing]] venue in [[Killarney]], [[County Kerry]], [[Republic of Ireland|Ireland]] which stages both [[National Hunt]] and [[Flat racing]]. Racing at Killarney has been taking place since 1822. The course is a left-handed oval, one mile and two furlongs in circumference.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goracing.ie/HRI/Whats-On/Racecourses/Killarney/ |title=Course Profile|date=|publisher=Go Racing|accessdate=19 September 2012 }}</ref>

