'''Zuwara Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Zuwara]], [[Libya]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Aljazeera Sports Club]].  The stadium holds 2,000 people.

